<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - Watch Store</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #555;
            margin: 0;
        }

       .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 20px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    display: block; /* Explicitly define block layout */
}

.section {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: block; /* Ensure block layout for each section */
}


        .section h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #222;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .section p {
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .cookie-banner {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .cookie-banner a {
            color: #00aaff;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 15px;
            }

            header h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }

            .section h2 {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .section p {
                font-size: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<header id="header" class="navbar">
  <div class="logo">chronara</div>
  <nav>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="/user/home">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/user/getContactPage">Contact</a></li>
      <li><a href="/user/getAboutPage">About</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
  {{#if username}}
    <div class="dropdown">
      <a class="sign-in-link" href="#">{{username}}</a>
      <div class="dropdown-content">
        <a href="/user/profile">Profile</a>
        <a href="/user/logout">Logout</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  {{else}}
    <div class="auth-links">
      <a href="/user/login">Login</a> | <a href="/user/usersignup">Signup</a>
    </div>
  {{/if}}
</header>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>We at Watch Store are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal data.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect personal information such as your name, email, shipping address, and payment details to process your orders and enhance your experience.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>Your information is used to process transactions, personalize your experience, and improve our services.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
        <p>We may share your information with trusted third parties like payment processors and shipping providers.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. Please contact us to make such requests.</p>
    </div>
</div>

{{>userfooter}}



</body>
</html>
